- Bukan.

267
00:21:34,203 --> 00:21:36,330
Tak ada tugas hingga kita tiba
di Jerman.

268
00:21:36,414 --> 00:21:38,499
Sayang sekali.

269
00:21:40,167 --> 00:21:42,003
Siapa komandanmu?

