00:32:08,874 --> 00:32:10,751
Paris!

411
00:32:12,044 --> 00:32:13,879
Paris.

412
00:32:32,064 --> 00:32:33,649
Apa aku telat?

413
00:32:34,567 --> 00:32:36,193
Sekitar empat tahun.

414
00:32:36,277 --> 00:32:38,863
- Apa kabar, James?
- Halo, Rene.

415
00:32:38,946 --> 00:32:41,032
Berapa banyak karya seni
yang kalian selamatkan?

