00:53:32,482 --> 00:53:35,485
DESEMBER, 1944
PERTEMPURAN BULGE

640
00:53:58,008 --> 00:54:03,180
<i>♪ Kau selalu menyakiti ♪</i>

641
00:54:03,263 --> 00:54:08,352
